    'month' => '01',
    'body' => 'On Mon, 15 Jan 1996 traveller@mpgn.com said:

>Date: Thu, 11 Jan 1996 16:08:32 -0600 (CST)
>From: James Kiley <tenzil@io.com>
>To: Traveller ML <traveller@MPGN.COM>
